actions.name: AssociateServiceRoleToAccount
actions.description: Associates the user's account with IAM roles controlling various permissions needed by AWS DeepLens for proper functionality.

actions.name: BatchGetDevice
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens devices.

actions.name: BatchGetModel
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens Models.

actions.name: BatchGetProject
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens Projects.

actions.name: CreateDeviceCertificates
actions.description: Creates a certificate package that is used to successfully authenticate and Register an AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: CreateModel
actions.description: Creates a new AWS DeepLens Model.

actions.name: CreateProject
actions.description: Creates a new AWS DeepLens Project.

actions.name: DeleteModel
actions.description: Deletes an AWS DeepLens Model.

actions.name: DeleteProject
actions.description: Deletes an AWS DeepLens Project.

actions.name: DeployProject
actions.description: Deploys an AWS DeepLens project to a registered AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: DeregisterDevice
actions.description: Begins a device de-registration workflow for a registered AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: GetAssociatedResources
actions.description: Retrieves the account level resources associated with the user's account.

actions.name: GetDeploymentStatus
actions.description: Retrieves the the deployment status of a particular AWS DeepLens device, along with any associated metadata.

actions.name: GetDevice
actions.description: Retrieves information about an AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: GetModel
actions.description: Retrieves an AWS DeepLens Model.

actions.name: GetProject
actions.description: Retrieves an AWS DeepLens Project.

actions.name: ImportProjectFromTemplate
actions.description: Creates a new AWS DeepLens project from a sample project template.

actions.name: ListDeployments
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens Deployment identifiers.

actions.name: ListDevices
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens device identifiers.

actions.name: ListModels
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens Model identifiers.

actions.name: ListProjects
actions.description: Retrieves a list of AWS DeepLens Project identifiers.

actions.name: RegisterDevice
actions.description: Begins a device registration workflow for an AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: RemoveProject
actions.description: Removes a deployed AWS DeepLens project from an AWS DeepLens device.

actions.name: UpdateProject
actions.description: Updates an existing AWS DeepLens Project.
